# OPTIONAL on a machine where you're logged into Claude Code — the Agent SDK
# uses the local `claude` login automatically. Set this only for headless or
# deployed runs: `claude setup-token` (1-year token, tied to your Claude
# subscription; draws from the plan's monthly Agent SDK credit — no API billing).
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# SIDECAR_PORT=4601
# SIDECAR_HOST=127.0.0.1      # keep on localhost — genproxy owns the public rails
# SIDECAR_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5
